        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold d-flex align-items-center gap-2" href="/">
            <img src="logo.png" alt="Yarpa" height="32" class="rounded" />
            <span>Yarpa Support</span>
        </a>
        <span class="text-white-50 small">לוח בקרה תמיכה</span>
